## The name

Apache-2.0 grants no rights to the project name (see its §6). "Ops4Jira" — the name
and any associated identity — is **not** part of the license grant. Fork and build on
the code freely, but please don't release a fork, product, or company *as* "Ops4Jira."
Saying your tool is *based on* or *a fork of* Ops4Jira is fine. See [`NOTICE`](NOTICE).

"Jira" is a trademark of Atlassian. Ops4Jira is not affiliated with or endorsed by
Atlassian; the name uses "Jira" referentially to describe what the tool works with.

